biography: Shivam is an open source developer. He has experience working remotely with open source projects like Mozilla Firefox, CNCF, Linux foundation and building communities. He loves to mentor folks get started with open source. He writes blogs at https://itsopensource.com/, maintains Documentation of Firefox https://firefox-source-docs.mozilla.org/. He also loves to travel, teach, and speak about open source and advocates for Diversity in Tech.
